<section class="strategy" style="padding: 150px 0; background: #000; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 100px;">
            <p
                style="color: #00F0FF; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase;">
                Synergy Ecosystem</p>
            <h2 class="section-title">Win-Win GROWTH STRATEGY</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="synergy-wrapper" style="position: relative; max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; min-height: 600px;">
            <!-- SVG Paths for Energy Flow -->
            <svg class="energy-svg" viewBox="0 0 1000 600"
                style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1;">
                <!-- Studio Center (500, 100) -> Brand Center (150, 450) -->
                <path id="path-studio-brand" d="M500,100 L150,450" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2)"
                    stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="1000" stroke-dashoffset="1000" />
                <!-- Studio Center (500, 100) -> Creator Center (850, 450) -->
                <path id="path-studio-creator" d="M500,100 L850,450" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2)"
                    stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="1000" stroke-dashoffset="1000" />
                <!-- Brand Center (150, 450) -> Creator Center (850, 450) -->
                <path id="path-brand-creator" d="M150,450 Q500,520 850,450" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2)"
                    stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="1000" stroke-dashoffset="1000" />

                <!-- Animated Energy Dots -->
                <circle r="4" fill="#00F0FF">
                    <animateMotion dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite" path="M500,100 L150,450" />
                </circle>
                <circle r="4" fill="#00F0FF">
                    <animateMotion dur="3s" repeatCount="indefinite" path="M500,100 L850,450" />
                </circle>
                <circle r="4" fill="#00F0FF">
                    <animateMotion dur="4s" repeatCount="indefinite" path="M150,450 Q500,520 850,450" />
                </circle>
            </svg>

            <!-- Strategy Nodes -->
            <!-- Center at 500px: Node width 300px, so left = 500 - 150 = 350px -->
            <div class="strategy-node node-studio" style="position: absolute; top: 30px; left: 350px; z-index: 2;">
                <div class="node-circle">DONGDONG<br>STUDIO</div>
                <div class="node-content center">
                    <p>콘텐츠로 브랜드와 크리에이터를 연결하고,<br>기업 브랜딩과 퍼널 브랜딩 가치를 함께 높이며<br>장기적인 협업을 통해 수익화를 극대화합니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Center at 150px: Node width 300px, so left = 150 - 150 = 0px -->
            <div class="strategy-node node-brand" style="position: absolute; top: 380px; left: 0px; z-index: 2;">
                <div class="node-circle">BRAND</div>
                <div class="node-content left">
                    <p>브랜드에 가장 적합한 크리에이터를 매칭하고,<br>브랜드 방향과 마케팅 전략을 기획해<br>지속적인 매출과 브랜드 가치를 높입니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Center at 850px: Node width 300px, so left = 850 - 150 = 700px -->
            <div class="strategy-node node-creator" style="position: absolute; top: 380px; left: 700px; z-index: 2;">
                <div class="node-circle">CREATOR</div>
                <div class="node-content right">
                    <p>크리에이터의 개성과 강점을 발굴하고,<br>콘텐츠 방향과 성장 로드맵을 설계해<br>지속적인 팔로워 성장과 수익 모델을 만들어갑니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

